Part 1: Language Overview

1.1 Two-Language Architecture

```yaml
maia:
  type: compiled
  paradigm: multi
  memory: no_gc + compile_time_rc
  safety: borrow_checker + reference_capabilities
  concurrency: actors + channels + async/await
  targets: [x86_64, arm64, riscv64, wasm32]
  ffi: [c, cpp, rust, zig, pony, java, python, objective_c]

koda:
  type: interpreted
  paradigm: multi
  modes: [embedded, standalone_shell]
  features: [async_await, templates, vcs, orm, web_framework]
  ffi: via_maia
```

1.2 Shared Syntax Principles

```yaml
syntax:
  style: pascal
  blocks: begin...end
  comments: "//" and "(* *)"
  case_sensitive: true
  semicolons: required
  whitespace: insignificant
```

